<TEXT>
Pepper prices are considerably ahead of the extremely low levels of a few
months ago, reports Man-producten. Large scale short covering in the main
origin countries has pushed domestic prices much higher, but this has not
resulted in very active trading in consuming markets - most buyers prefer to
wait and see. There were hardly any offers available from Brazil although it
