59.9m in the third quarter of 1991.
Net profits for the first nine months of 1992 were Dollars 14.6m, down from
Dollars 44.2m in the same period last year.
Revenues were Dollars 402.3m, up from Dollars 396.4m, while R&amp;D spending was
Dollars 208.9m, up from Dollars 161.6m.
On Wall Street, Genentech's stock price was Dollars  1/8 higher at Dollars
33 1/4.
