local management. The consideration is a nominal Dollars 200,000; but a
package has been agreed under which the group will retain a minority
interest, carrying 19 per cent of the voting rights.
In the group accounts there is an extraordinary charge of IPounds 6.5m
representing IPounds 4.5m to cover the package and the write off of the
investment, plus IPounds 2m for goodwill.
Earnings per share for the half year came to 6.9p (17.1p).
